Why should you secure your browser?  Not securing your web browser can lead quickly to a variety of computer problems caused by anything from spyware being installed without your knowledge to intruders taking control of your computer.
Cookies leave sort of a bread crumb trail where you've been is you don't close browsers your are esentially leaving something open. A hacker find one of these cookies and revisit somewhere you have been. also companies use these cookies to store data about you legally so it is a good idea to shut your computer down properly to help avoid these issues in the future.
